profile_positions.description:
You have to know, I find it difficult to pick one single activity. 
And, if I really think about it, I don't want to.

So I picked one goal: to help sustainable and positive entrepreneurs: 
- to optimize their natural referencing of their website thanks to SEO web writing; 
- to develop and maintain their podcast with complete peace of mind; 
- to feel lighter by refocusing their time, their concentration and their energy on the heart of their activity

👨‍💻 I suggest you call on me for the following missions: 
- writing in French the content of your website and your blog articles; 
- English -> French translation; 
- proofreading and optimization of existing content; 
- content integration on WordPress; 
- podcast management (audit, editing of episodes with addition of intro and outro, writing descriptions, planning, creation and recycling of content for Instagram and LinkedIn, transcription, organization of interviews, etc.); 
- animation of your community; 
- organization of strategic brainstorming to decide on the next steps in the development of your business.
